high_descs: Turn left to walk to the microwave.
Take the green apple out of the microwave.
Take a right to walk to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk back to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash an apple from the microwave to put it back.

high_descs: take the apple out of the microwave
take the cooked apple to the sink
rinse the apple in the sink
take the apple back to the microwave
put the apple back in the microwave
anns.task_desc: rinse and apple to put it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and when you get to the black bar stool, head left again and cross the kitchen to stand at the counter above the dishwasher.
Open the microwave door above the counter and remove the green apple
Turn right and carry the apple to the sink.
Place the apple in the right sink, turn on the water, and then remove once washed.
Turn left and carry the apple back to the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed apple in the microwave.
